author: rbb
msg: Mote the testucs.c file from test/ to test/internal/.  The testucs program
specifically tests internals of APR that are not exported.  This is a good
thing, but the test/ directory is for testing APR externals so that APR
developers can ensure that their port of APR works correctly.  For testing
APR internals, there is now a separate directory.
